msgctxt "EXPLANATION_0"
msgid ""
"１年ぶりの土佐だ。皆、変わりないだろうか……\n"
"少し街をぶらつくとしよう。"
msgstr ""
"It's Tosa for the first time in a year. Will everyone change ... Let's "
"wander around the city a little."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_1"
msgid ""
"土佐の連中は相変わらずのようだな。\n"
"こいつらごとき、刀を振るまでもない。\n"
"拳で黙らせてやる……！"
msgstr ""
"It seems that the Tosa guys are still the same. You don't have to swing your"
" sword like these guys. I'll shut it up with my fist ...!"

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_3"
msgid ""
"さて、そろそろ親っさんの所へ向かおう。\n"
"「牽牛子塾」と言っていたな。\n"
"誰かに場所を訊いてみるか……"
msgstr ""
"Well, let's head to the parents' place. You used to say \"Kengoshizuka "
"Juku\". Would you like to ask someone for a place ..."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_4"
msgid ""
"「牽牛子塾」は千歳屋の裏手にあるらしい。\n"
"どうやらかなりわかりづらい場所みたいだな。\n"
"裏手に回れる路地がないか探してみるか……"
msgstr ""
"It seems that \"Kengoshizuka Juku\" is behind Chitoseya. Apparently it's a "
"pretty confusing place. Do you want to find an alley behind you ..."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_5"
msgid ""
"恨みを買ってしまったようだ……\n"
"事が大きくならないうちに黙らせるしかなさそうだな。"
msgstr ""
"It seems that he has bought a grudge ... It seems that he has no choice but "
"to shut up before things get bigger."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_6"
msgid ""
"千歳屋の横から裏手に回れそうだな。\n"
"「牽牛子塾」へ向かおう。"
msgstr ""
"It looks like you can go behind the scenes from the side of Chitoseya. Let's"
" head to \"Kengoshizuka Juku\"."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_7"
msgid ""
"土佐勤王党か……　とにかく兄弟に会いに行くか。\n"
"どこにいるのか、街の奴にでも訊いてみよう。"
msgstr ""
"Is it the Tosa Qin Wang Party ... Anyway, do you go to see your brothers? "
"Ask the guys in town where you are."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_8"
msgid ""
"武市のいる武市道場はこの町の北東にあるらしい。\n"
"さっそく行ってみるか。"
msgstr ""
"The Takeshi Dojo, where Takeshi is located, seems to be in the northeast of "
"this town. Would you like to go right away?"

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_9"
msgid ""
"土佐勤王党ってのは、案外面倒な集団らしい。\n"
"仕方がない、他に武市に会う方法がないか探るか。"
msgstr ""
"The Tosakino Party seems to be an unexpectedly troublesome group. There is "
"no choice but to find out if there is another way to meet Takeichi."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_10"
msgid ""
"勤王党ってのは名を借りる奴が出てくるほど\n"
"有名なのか……\n"
"腕試しがてら、さっさと片付けちまおう。"
msgstr ""
"Is the Qin Wang Party so famous that some people borrow its name ... Let's "
"get rid of it quickly after trying our skills."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_11"
msgid ""
"武市道場か……\n"
"階段を上がったところにあると言っていたな。\n"
"早速行ってみよう。"
msgstr "Takeshi Dojo ... You said it was up the stairs. Let's go immediately."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_12"
msgid ""
"さて、兄弟の支度がすむまでどうするかな……\n"
"通りの手ごろな店で\n"
"酒でも飲みながら時間を潰すか。"
msgstr ""
"Now, what do you do until your brothers are ready ... Do you want to kill "
"time while drinking alcohol at an affordable store on the street?"

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_13"
msgid ""
"さっき党員を語って悪さを働いていた奴の仲間か。\n"
"まったくロクでもない奴らだな……"
msgstr ""
"Is it a companion of the guy who talked about the party members and worked "
"badly? Those guys who aren't at all ..."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_14"
msgid ""
"そろそろいい時間だ。\n"
"武市道場へ戻ってみよう。"
msgstr "It's about time. Let's go back to the Takeshi Dojo."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_15"
msgid ""
"岡田以蔵、と言ったか……\n"
"こいつには本気で挑んだ方がよさそうだ。"
msgstr ""
"Did you say Okada Izo ... It seems better to challenge this guy seriously."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_16"
msgid ""
"兄弟と高知城へ行くんだったな。\n"
"何があるか分からない……\n"
"できる準備はしてから出発するとしよう。"
msgstr ""
"I was going to Kochi Castle with my brother. I don't know what's going on "
"... Let's say you're ready to start."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_17"
msgid ""
"兄弟が高知城まで案内してくれるという。\n"
"今は後をついて行くとしよう。"
msgstr ""
"It is said that the brothers will guide you to Kochi Castle. Let's follow "
"for now."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_18"
msgid ""
"親っさんが殺られた……!?\n"
"あの覆面の男、一体何者なんだ……!!"
msgstr "My parents were killed ...!? Who the hell is that masked man ... !!"

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_19"
msgid ""
"こいつが親っさんを……\n"
"このまま逃すわけにはいかない!!"
msgstr "This guy can't miss his parents ... as it is !!"

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_20"
msgid ""
"第一章「土佐、脱藩」～完～\n"
"第二章「斎藤一という男」へ……"
msgstr "To Chapter 1 \"Tosa, Dappan\" -End-Chapter 2 \"A Man named Saito Hajime\" ..."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_21"
msgid ""
"まったく、おちおち寝てもいられないな……\n"
"そろそろ出かけるとするか。"
msgstr "I can't sleep at all ... Shall I go out soon?"

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_22"
msgid ""
"これ以上ここにいても、何の収穫もなさそうだ。\n"
"さっさと黙らせて他を当たろう。"
msgstr ""
"There seems to be no harvest if I stay here any longer. Let's shut up and "
"hit the others."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_23"
msgid ""
"あの情報屋も大して期待できそうにないな。\n"
"少し町を歩き回ってみるか……"
msgstr ""
"That information shop doesn't seem to be very promising either. Would you "
"like to walk around the town a little ..."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_25"
msgid ""
"京ほどの大きな町になると不届き者も\n"
"それなりにいるようだな。\n"
"さて、もう少し町を歩きまわるとしよう。"
msgstr ""
"When it comes to a town as big as Kyo, it seems that there are some "
"undelivered people. Now, let's walk around the town a little more."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_26"
msgid ""
"厄介事は御免だ。\n"
"どこかに隠れてやり過ごせるといいんだが……"
msgstr ""
"I'm sorry for the trouble. I hope I can hide somewhere and go through ..."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_27"
msgid ""
"夜までまだ時間があるな。\n"
"寺田屋に戻って暇をつぶそう。"
msgstr ""
"I still have time until night. Let's go back to Teradaya and kill time."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_28"
msgid ""
"屋敷町南にある風呂屋に行くとしよう。\n"
"何があるか分からない……\n"
"準備は十分にしておいた方がよさそうだ。"
msgstr ""
"Let's say you go to a bathhouse in the south of Yashikicho. I don't know "
"what's going on ... I think it's better to be well prepared."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_29"
msgid ""
"喧嘩するいわれはないが、\n"
"こうなったら負けるわけにはいかねぇな。"
msgstr "I'm not told to quarrel, but I can't afford to lose if this happens."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_30"
msgid "今日はもう寺田屋に戻って休むとしよう。"
msgstr "Let's go back to Teradaya and take a rest today."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_31"
msgid ""
"さっきの男……　いったい何者だ？\n"
"骸街（むくろがい）で待つと言っていたな。\n"
"寺田屋に戻って場所を確認するか……"
msgstr ""
"The man from earlier ... Who the hell are you? You said you would wait in "
"the skeleton town. Would you like to go back to Teradaya and check the "
"location ..."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_32"
msgid ""
"船頭が、骸街（むくろがい）まで舟を出してくれると\n"
"言っていたな。寺田屋で待っているはずだ。\n"
"準備ができたら声をかけるか。"
msgstr ""
"The captain said that he would take the boat to Mukurogai. You should be "
"waiting at Teradaya. Would you like to call out when you're ready?"

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_33"
msgid ""
"ここが骸街（むくろがい）か。\n"
"さっきの男は見当たらないが……\n"
"とりあえず奥へ進んでみよう。"
msgstr ""
"Is this a skeleton town? I can't find the man I just mentioned, but ... "
"let's go deeper for the time being."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_34"
msgid ""
"編み笠の男は以蔵だったのか……\n"
"そっちがその気なら、受けて立つしかないな。"
msgstr ""
"Was the man in the knitting hat Izo ... If that was the case, I would have "
"to accept it."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_35"
msgid ""
"兄弟は骸街（むくろがい）の一番奥にいるらしい。\n"
"まさか会えるとは思っていなかったな……\n"
"久しぶりだが、元気にしていただろうか。"
msgstr ""
"The brothers seem to be in the innermost part of Mukurogai. I didn't expect "
"to see you ... It's been a while, but I wonder if I'm fine."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_36"
msgid ""
"さて、特にこの後の予定もない……\n"
"自由に京の町を散策するとしよう。"
msgstr ""
"By the way, I have no plans after this ... Let's take a walk around the town"
" of Kyoto freely."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_37"
msgid ""
"第二章「斎藤一」～完～\n"
"第三章「壬生狼」へ……"
msgstr "Chapter 2 \"Saito Hajime\" -End-To Chapter 3 \"Mibu Wolf\" ..."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_38"
msgid ""
"確か新選組の屯所は四条通りを西へ行った所だったな。\n"
"お登勢たちの話だと、かなり粗暴な奴ららしい。\n"
"準備はしっかりしていった方がよさそうだな。"
msgstr ""
"Certainly, the Shinsengumi tunsho was the place where I went west on Shijo-"
"dori. According to the story of the ascendants, they seem to be quite rough."
" It seems better to be well prepared."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_39"
msgid ""
"これが天念理心流……!!　こいつが\n"
"親っさんの仇という可能性もあるという事か。\n"
"心して挑む必要がありそうだな……"
msgstr ""
"This is Tennen Rishin-ryu …… !! Is it possible that this is the soul of his "
"parents? I think we need to challenge ourselves ..."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_40"
msgid ""
"新選組には天念理心流の使い手が何人かいるようだ。\n"
"沖田という男もまだ覆面の男である可能性がある……\n"
"いろいろ確かめる必要がありそうだ。"
msgstr ""
"It seems that there are several users of Tennen Rishin-ryu in the "
"Shinsengumi. There is a possibility that a man named Okita is still a masked"
" man ... It seems that we need to confirm various things."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_41"
msgid ""
"日も暮れてきた。\n"
"土方が言っていた料亭へ向かおう。\n"
"確か祗園にある椿楼という店だったな。"
msgstr ""
"The sun has set. Let's head to the restaurant Hijikata said. I'm sure it was"
" a store called Tsubakiro in Gion."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_42"
msgid ""
"これも試験の一環という訳か……\n"
"気は進まないが、\n"
"ここで引き下がるわけにもいかないな。"
msgstr ""
"Is this also part of the exam ... I'm reluctant, but I can't withdraw here."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_43"
msgid ""
"第三章「壬生狼」～完～\n"
"第四章「共闘」へ……"
msgstr "Chapter 3 \"Mibu Wolf\"~End~ Chapter 4 \"Kongyin\"へ……"

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_44"
msgid ""
"覆面の男である可能性が一番高い近藤勇には\n"
"今日はお目にかかれなかったな。\n"
"まあ、まだ機会はこれからいくらでもあるだろう。"
msgstr ""
"I didn't see Isami Kondo, who is most likely a masked man, today. Well, "
"there are still plenty of opportunities."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_45"
msgid ""
"新選組の隊長が着ている羽織……\n"
"明日からこれを着て仕事をするという訳か。\n"
"とりあえず今日は寺田屋に戻るとしよう。"
msgstr ""
"Haori worn by the captain of the Shinsengumi ... Will you be wearing this to"
" work from tomorrow? For the time being, let's return to Teradaya today."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_46"
msgid ""
"軽く、この家の設備でも確認してみるか。\n"
"まずは庭からだな。"
msgstr ""
"It's light, so why don't you check the equipment in this house? First of "
"all, from the garden."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_47"
msgid "この家の屋内の設備を確認してみるか。"
msgstr "Would you like to check the indoor equipment of this house?"

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_48"
msgid ""
"かなり時間を食ってしまったな……\n"
"とりあえず今日は寺田屋に戻るとしよう。"
msgstr "It took a lot of time ... Let's go back to Teradaya today."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_49"
msgid ""
"おりょうの奴、どこに行ったんだ……\n"
"女将さんは鴨川じゃないかと言っていたが……\n"
"他にあてもないし、探しに行ってみるか。"
msgstr ""
"Where did you go ... The proprietress said it was Kamogawa, but ... there's "
"nothing else, so why don't you go find it?"

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_50"
msgid ""
"おりょうは分かってくれたようだな。\n"
"俺も寺田屋に戻ろう。"
msgstr "It seems that you understand. Let's go back to Teradaya."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_51"
msgid ""
"土佐なまりの男……　一体誰だ？\n"
"何かの罠かもしれないな。\n"
"十分に準備してから清水寺に向かおう。"
msgstr ""
"Tosa Namari's man ... Who the hell is that? It might be some kind of trap. "
"Let's prepare enough before heading to Kiyomizu Temple."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_52"
msgid ""
"こんな所でやられるわけにはいかない……\n"
"こいつらを倒して清水寺から出なくては！"
msgstr ""
"I can't do it in a place like this ... I have to defeat them and get out of "
"Kiyomizu-dera!"

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_53"
msgid ""
"第四章「共闘」～完～\n"
"第五章「鉄の掟」へ……"
msgstr "Chapter 4 \"Co-op\" -End-To Chapter 5 \"Rules of Iron\" ..."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_54"
msgid ""
"新選組の屯所へ向かうとしよう。\n"
"今日は、藤堂から仕事の説明をしてもらう事に\n"
"なっていたはずだ。"
msgstr ""
"Let's say we're heading to the Shinsengumi tunsho. I should have had Todo "
"explain my work today."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_55"
msgid ""
"藤堂が屯所内の案内をしてくれるらしい。\n"
"今は説明を聞いて早く覚えなくては……"
msgstr ""
"It seems that Todo will guide you inside the tunsho. Now I have to listen to"
" the explanation and remember it soon ..."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_56"
msgid ""
"もう夕方か……\n"
"今日のところは寺田屋に帰るとしよう。"
msgstr "It's already evening ... Let's go back to Teradaya for today."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_57"
msgid ""
"新選組に入ってからの初仕事だな。\n"
"例の脱走隊士は祗園の日向屋で飲んでいるらしい。\n"
"早速向かおう。"
msgstr ""
"It's my first job since joining the Shinsengumi. It seems that the escape "
"soldier in the example is drinking at Hinataya in Gion. Let's head right "
"away."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_58"
msgid ""
"藤堂が出入り口の見張りにつくらしい。\n"
"乗り込むときは藤堂に声をかけてやるか。"
msgstr ""
"It seems that Todo will be on guard at the doorway. Do you call Todo when "
"you get in?"

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_59"
msgid ""
"この秋元という男……　ロクな奴じゃないな。\n"
"性根を叩き直してやろう。"
msgstr ""
"This guy named Akimoto ... I'm not a good guy. Let's beat the sex roots "
"again."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_60"
msgid ""
"副長の土方に報告に行かなければ。\n"
"新選組の屯所へ向かうとしよう。"
msgstr ""
"I have to go to report to Deputy Director Hijikata. Let's say we're heading "
"to the Shinsengumi tunsho."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_61"
msgid ""
"谷や鈴木より先に以蔵を捕らえなくては……\n"
"洛外の賭場にいると言っていたな。……急ごう!!"
msgstr ""
"I had to catch Izo before Taniya and Suzuki ... He said he was in the "
"Rakugai gambling house. ...... Hurry up !!"

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_62"
msgid ""
"くそっ。谷が先に行ってしまった。\n"
"こんなところで足止めをくっている場合じゃない。\n"
"さっさと倒して追いかけなくては……！"
msgstr ""
"Damn. The valley has gone first. It's not the case when you're stuck in a "
"place like this. I have to defeat it quickly and chase after it ...!"

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_63"
msgid ""
"以蔵……　闘いたくはないが致し方ないか……\n"
"向こうが本気で来る以上、こちらも手は抜けない。\n"
"真剣にやるしかなさそうだな……！"
msgstr ""
"Izo ... I don't want to fight, but I can't help it ... As long as the other "
"side really comes, I can't help it either. I think I have to do it seriously"
" ...!"

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_64"
msgid ""
"夜も更けてきたな……\n"
"とりあえず寺田屋に戻ろう。"
msgstr "It's late at night ... Let's go back to Teradaya for the time being."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_65"
msgid ""
"第五章「鉄の掟」～完～\n"
"第六章「池田屋事件」へ……"
msgstr "To Chapter 5 \"Rules of Iron\" -End-Chapter 6 \"Ikedaya Incident\" ..."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_66"
msgid ""
"今日の幹部会での話……\n"
"中岡の名が出ていたのが気になるな。\n"
"寺田屋に戻って中岡に知らせてやろう。"
msgstr ""
"Talk at today's presidium ... I'm curious that Nakaoka was mentioned. Let's "
"go back to Teradaya and let Nakaoka know."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_67"
msgid ""
"中岡は寺田屋の二階にいるらしい。\n"
"今日の幹部会での話をしよう。"
msgstr ""
"Nakaoka seems to be on the second floor of Teradaya. Let's talk about "
"today's presidium."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_68"
msgid ""
"とりあえず今のところは中岡がうまく\n"
"やってくれるのを願うしかなさそうだな。"
msgstr "For now, I can only hope that Nakaoka will do it well."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_69"
msgid ""
"そろそろ屯所に戻って今夜の襲撃に備えなくてはな。\n"
"戻る前にできる準備はしておこう。"
msgstr ""
"It's time to go back to the tunsho and prepare for the raid tonight. Get "
"ready before you go back."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_70"
msgid ""
"屯所に待機するようにとの指示だ。\n"
"他の隊長らと話でもしてみるか。"
msgstr ""
"It is an instruction to wait at the tunsho. Would you like to talk to other "
"captains?"

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_71"
msgid ""
"土方からの呼び出しらしい。\n"
"土蔵へ向かおう。"
msgstr "It seems to be a call from Hijikata. Let's head to the storehouse."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_72"
msgid ""
"出陣だ。三番隊の持ち場は四国屋だったな。\n"
"洛内の南東にある四国屋へ向かおう。"
msgstr ""
"It's time to start. The place of the third corps was Shikokuya. Let's head "
"to Shikokuya in the southeast of Rakuchu."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_73"
msgid ""
"勤王志士らの会合は池田屋の方だったらしい。\n"
"急いで向かわなくては……"
msgstr ""
"It seems that the meeting of the Qin Wang Shishi was from Ikedaya. I have to"
" hurry up ..."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_74"
msgid ""
"中岡はうまく伝えられなかったようだな。\n"
"仕方がない、吉田稔麿と桂小五郎を探そう！"
msgstr ""
"Nakaoka didn't seem to be able to communicate well. Let's find Minoru "
"Yoshida and Kogoro Katsura that can't be helped!"

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_75"
msgid ""
"永倉程の男がやられるとは……\n"
"この吉田という男、油断できないな。"
msgstr ""
"It is said that a man like Nagakura will be killed ... This man named "
"Yoshida cannot be alert."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_76"
msgid ""
"あとは桂小五郎か。\n"
"逃がす訳にはいかない、早く見つけなくては！"
msgstr ""
"The rest is Kogoro Katsura. I can't let it go, I have to find it soon!"

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_77"
msgid ""
"くそっ、面倒な事になったな。\n"
"とりあえずはコイツに付き合ってやるか……"
msgstr ""
"Damn, it's a hassle. For the time being, do you want to go out with this guy"
" ..."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_78"
msgid ""
"第六章「池田屋事件」～完～\n"
"第七章「二人の龍馬」へ……"
msgstr "Chapter 6 \"Ikedaya Incident\" -End-To Chapter 7 \"Two Ryoma\" ..."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_79"
msgid ""
"まだ一度も局長の近藤の姿を見ていない。\n"
"機会を逃さないためにも、\n"
"屯所には顔を出しておかなくては……"
msgstr ""
"I have never seen the director, Kondo. In order not to miss the opportunity,"
" I have to show my face to the tunsho ..."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_80"
msgid ""
"局長である近藤の部屋は、屯所の一番奥の間だと\n"
"言っていたな。\n"
"不在かもしれないが、見に行ってみよう。"
msgstr ""
"You said that Kondo's room, the director, is the innermost room of the "
"tunsho. It may be absent, but let's go see it."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_81"
msgid ""
"他に、局長について話を聞けそうな奴はいないか？\n"
"副長である土方なら何か知っているかもしれないな。\n"
"土方の部屋に行ってみよう。"
msgstr ""
"Is there anyone else who could talk to the director? Hijikata, the deputy "
"director, may know something. Let's go to Hijikata's room."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_82"
msgid ""
"特に情報は得られなかったな。\n"
"やはり近藤に会うのは一筋縄ではいかないか。\n"
"他に話が聞けそうなやつはいないか探してみるか。"
msgstr ""
"I didn't get any information. Isn't it easy to meet Kondo? Would you like to"
" find someone else you could talk to?"

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_83"
msgid ""
"誰も近藤に会う方法を知らない様だ。\n"
"ひとまず屯所を出て探ってみるか。"
msgstr ""
"No one seems to know how to meet Kondo. Do you want to go out of the tunsho "
"and explore it for the time being?"

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_84"
msgid ""
"坂本龍馬を探れ、だと!?　俺の偽物なのか……？\n"
"中岡なら何か知っているかもしれない。\n"
"一度、寺田屋に戻ろう。"
msgstr ""
"Search for Ryoma Sakamoto !? Is it my fake ...? Nakaoka may know something. "
"Let's go back to Teradaya once."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_85"
msgid ""
"もう一人の坂本龍馬についての情報を集めなくては。\n"
"まずは薩摩藩邸に行って、西郷から話を聞こう。"
msgstr ""
"I have to collect information about another Ryoma Sakamoto. First, let's go "
"to the Satsuma clan's residence and hear from Saigo."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_86"
msgid ""
"簡単には中に入れてはもらえないという訳か。\n"
"仕方がない……\n"
"ここは力で押し切るしかなさそうだ。"
msgstr ""
"Doesn't it mean that you can't easily put it inside? It can't be helped ... "
"It seems that there is no choice but to push it through with force."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_87"
msgid ""
"局長の近藤からの呼び出し……\n"
"この機会、逃すわけにはいかないな。\n"
"急いで、祗園にある旭屋（あさひや）へ向かおう。"
msgstr ""
"Call from Director Kondo ... I can't miss this opportunity. Let's hurry to "
"Asahiya in Gion."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_88"
msgid ""
"やはり近藤があの覆面の男だったのか……？\n"
"……それも刀を交えればわかることだ!!"
msgstr ""
"Was Kondo the masked man ...? ...... You can understand that with a sword !!"

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_89"
msgid ""
"第七章「二人の龍馬」～完～\n"
"第八章「狂犬吠える」へ……"
msgstr "To Chapter 7 \"Two Ryoma\" -End-Chapter 8 \"Mad Dog Barking\" ..."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_90"
msgid ""
"近藤は覆面の男ではなかった。\n"
"残るは土方、沖田、井上、藤堂か……\n"
"当てはないが屯所には顔を出しておこう。"
msgstr ""
"Kondo was not a masked man. The rest are Hijikata, Okita, Inoue, Todo ... I "
"don't know, but let's show up at the tunsho."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_91"
msgid ""
"沖田が話があるとか言っていたな……\n"
"一体何だろうか？\n"
"土蔵へ行ってみるとするか。"
msgstr ""
"Okita said he had a story ... what the heck? Would you like to go to the "
"storehouse?"

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_92"
msgid ""
"沖田は夜になったら千石邸へ来いと言っていたな。\n"
"寺田屋で夜まで時間を潰すとするか。"
msgstr ""
"Okita said he would come to Sengoku's house at night. Do you want to kill "
"time at Teradaya until night?"

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_93"
msgid ""
"沖田は千石邸の前で待っていると言っていたな。\n"
"伏見に豪邸を構えてるらしい。\n"
"……となれば屋敷町の辺りか。早速向かおう。"
msgstr ""
"Okita said he was waiting in front of the Sengoku residence. It seems that "
"he has a mansion in Fushimi. ...... Is it around Yashiki-cho? Let's head "
"right away."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_94"
msgid ""
"千石邸の前で沖田が待っている。\n"
"討ち入りの準備ができたら声をかけよう。"
msgstr ""
"Okita is waiting in front of the Sengoku residence. Call out when you're "
"ready to slaughter."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_95"
msgid ""
"標的はこの屋敷の主、千石虎之丞……\n"
"さっさと見つけて終わらせよう。"
msgstr ""
"The target is Toranosuke Sengoku, the owner of this mansion ... Let's find "
"it quickly and finish it."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_96"
msgid ""
"沖田があの覆面の男だったのか!?\n"
"もし本当にそうだとしたら……\n"
"許すわけにはいかない!!"
msgstr "Was Okita the masked man !? If so ... I can't forgive him !!"

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_97"
msgid ""
"第八章「狂犬吠える」～完～\n"
"第九章「喧嘩の花道」へ……"
msgstr "Chapter 8 \"Mad Dog Barking\" -End-To Chapter 9 \"Fighting Flower Road\" ..."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_98"
msgid ""
"まだ飲み足りないな……\n"
"近場でどこか酒が飲める店へ行くか。\n"
"とりあえず外へ出よう。"
msgstr ""
"I haven't had enough to drink yet ... Would you like to go to a store where "
"you can drink alcohol nearby? Let's go outside for the time being."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_99"
msgid ""
"まだ飲み足りないな……\n"
"伏見一番街南の福々屋に行ってみるか。"
msgstr ""
"I haven't had enough to drink yet ... Would you like to go to Fukufukuya in "
"the south of Fushimi Ichibangai?"

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_100"
msgid ""
"さっきの女、一体誰だ？\n"
"よくは分からないが、女の言っていた\n"
"蔵町にある松之井とやらへ行ってみるか。"
msgstr ""
"Who the hell is that woman? I'm not sure, but would you like to go to "
"Matsunoi and Yara in Kuramachi, where the woman said?"

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_101"
msgid ""
"今はとことん暴れたい気分だ。\n"
"こいつらなら相手に不足はない。\n"
"ここは本気で喧嘩してやろうじゃないか！"
msgstr ""
"Now I feel like I want to go wild. With these guys, there is no shortage of "
"opponents. Let's have a serious quarrel here!"

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_102"
msgid ""
"洛内に居酒屋があったな……\n"
"二人を連れて行って、とことん飲んでやろう。"
msgstr ""
"There was an izakaya in Rakuchu ... Let's take them and drink them "
"thoroughly."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_103"
msgid ""
"確か祗園にも飲める店があったな。\n"
"春日だったか……　さっそく向かおう。"
msgstr ""
"I'm sure there was a restaurant in Gion where you could drink. Was it Kasuga"
" ... Let's head right away."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_104"
msgid ""
"第九章「喧嘩の花道」～完～\n"
"第十章「正体」へ……"
msgstr "Chapter 9 \"Fighting Flower Road\" -End-To Chapter 10 \"Identity\" ..."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_105"
msgid ""
"昨晩はかなり飲んでしまったな。\n"
"今は自分なりにできる事をするしかなさそうだ。\n"
"まずは屯所に顔を出すか……"
msgstr ""
"I drank a lot last night. Now I have no choice but to do what I can. First "
"of all, do you show up at the tunsho ..."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_106"
msgid ""
"永倉の様子がおかしかったが、何かあったのか？\n"
"ひとまず屯所へ向かおう。"
msgstr ""
"The appearance of Nagakura was strange, but what happened? Let's head to the"
" tunsho for the time being."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_107"
msgid ""
"井上の死体が発見されたのは\n"
"伏見の屋敷町南の船着き場らしい。\n"
"沖田はおそらくそこへ向かったのだろう。急ごう。"
msgstr ""
"It seems that Inoue's corpse was found at the pier in the south of Fushimi's"
" mansion town. Okita probably went there. Let's hurry."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_108"
msgid ""
"沖田は骸街に一番隊を集めているらしい。\n"
"事が大きくならないうちに、\n"
"一番隊の暴走を止めなくては……！"
msgstr ""
"Okita seems to be gathering the most corps in the skeleton town. Before "
"things get bigger, I have to stop the runaway of the first corps ...!"

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_109"
msgid ""
"一番隊の奴ら……　襲ってこなくなったな。\n"
"沖田は骸街の中にいるようだ。沖田を探そう。"
msgstr ""
"The guys in the first corps ... I'm not attacking. Okita seems to be in the "
"skeleton. Let's find Okita."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_110"
msgid ""
"沖田は骸街東の本堂跡地で俺を待っているらしい。\n"
"沖田が何を考えているのか正直分からない。\n"
"用心して向かうとしよう……"
msgstr ""
"Okita seems to be waiting for me at the site of the main hall in the east of"
" the skeleton. I honestly don't know what Okita is thinking. Let's be "
"careful ..."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_111"
msgid ""
"井上があの覆面の男だった、だと……\n"
"それに沖田の言っている虚無僧は一体誰なんだ？\n"
"俺はこの勝負に勝って真実を知る必要がある！"
msgstr ""
"Inoue was that masked man ... And who is the Komuso Okita says? I need to "
"win this game and know the truth!"

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_112"
msgid ""
"もう一人の坂本龍馬が、寺田屋にいる！\n"
"伊東と武田がすでに向かっているらしい。\n"
"なんとか先回りして捕まえなくては！"
msgstr ""
"Another Ryoma Sakamoto is in Teradaya! It seems that Ito and Takeda are "
"already heading. I have to get ahead and catch it!"

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_113"
msgid ""
"何としてももう一人の坂本龍馬を見つけなくては！\n"
"この機会を逃すわけにはいかない……"
msgstr ""
"Anyway, I have to find another Ryoma Sakamoto! I can't miss this opportunity"
" ..."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_114"
msgid ""
"この虚無僧が、坂本龍馬なのか!?\n"
"この勝負、負けるわけにはいかないな。\n"
"なんとしても正体を暴かなくては！"
msgstr ""
"Is this Komuso Ryoma Sakamoto !? I can't afford to lose this game. I have to"
" reveal my true identity!"

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_115"
msgid ""
"一旦、寺田屋に戻るとしよう。\n"
"おりょうにも聞きたいことがあるしな……"
msgstr "Let's go back to Teradaya. I have something to ask you too ..."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_116"
msgid ""
"第十章「正体」～完～\n"
"第十一章「大博打」へ……"
msgstr "Chapter 10 \"Traditional Body\" ~ End~ Chapter 11 \"Big Bo Da\" へ..."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_117"
msgid ""
"昨晩、山崎が屯所で殺された。\n"
"口封じというわけか……\n"
"一度屯所に戻って状況を確認しよう。"
msgstr ""
"Yamazaki was killed at the tunsho last night. It's a mouth-sealing ... Let's"
" go back to the tunsho and check the situation."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_118"
msgid ""
"山崎の遺体はまだ土蔵にあるのか。\n"
"藤堂が現場を見聞しているらしい。\n"
"行ってみよう、話くらい聞けるだろう。"
msgstr ""
"Is Yamazaki's body still in the storehouse? It seems that Todo is watching "
"the scene. Let's go, you can hear the story."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_119"
msgid ""
"寺田屋に戻って夜明けを待とう。\n"
"その前に、できる準備はしておかなくては……\n"
"江戸への旅は何が起こるか分からないからな。"
msgstr ""
"Let's go back to Teradaya and wait for the dawn. Before that, I have to be "
"prepared to do it ... I don't know what will happen on my trip to Edo."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_120"
msgid ""
"明日は江戸へ立つ。準備はしっかりして\n"
"おかなくてはな。寺田屋のお登勢に、夜明け前に\n"
"起こしてもらえるよう頼んでから休もう。"
msgstr ""
"I will stand in Edo tomorrow. You have to be well prepared. Let's take a "
"rest after asking Teradaya to wake up before dawn."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_121"
msgid ""
"ここまで来たからには、意地でも\n"
"徳川慶喜公の所までたどり着かなくては！\n"
"ここでやられるわけにはいかない……！"
msgstr ""
"Now that you've come this far, you have to get to Tokugawa Yoshinobu's "
"place! I can't do it here ...!"

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_122"
msgid ""
"話を聞いてもらうには、\n"
"この勝負に勝つしかなさそうだな。\n"
"なら、相手が誰であれ全力で戦うまでだ！"
msgstr ""
"It seems that the only way to get the story heard is to win this game. Then,"
" no matter who your opponent is, you can fight with all your might!"

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_123"
msgid ""
"第十一章「大博打」～完～\n"
"第十二章「京炎上」へ……"
msgstr "Chapter 11 \"Da Bo Da\" ~ End~ Chapter 12 \"Jing Yan Shang\" へ..."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_124"
msgid ""
"おりょうとお登勢たちが心配だ！\n"
"急いで寺田屋へ行こう！"
msgstr "I'm worried about Ryo and the climbers! Let's hurry to Teradaya!"

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_125"
msgid ""
"誰もいない、か……\n"
"ちゃんと避難できているといいが、\n"
"念のため室内を確認しよう。"
msgstr ""
"Nobody is there ... I hope you have evacuated properly, but let's check the "
"room just in case."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_126"
msgid ""
"二人は無事に避難できたようだ。\n"
"一安心だな。\n"
"表で待たせてる沖田の所に戻ろう。"
msgstr ""
"It seems that the two were able to evacuate safely. I'm relieved. Let's go "
"back to Okita, who has been waiting at the table."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_127"
msgid ""
"新選組が火を放ったというのは本当なのだろうか？\n"
"とにかく、近藤を探して話を聞くしかなさそうだ。"
msgstr ""
"Is it true that the Shinsengumi set fire? Anyway, it seems that I have no "
"choice but to look for Kondo and listen to him."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_128"
msgid ""
"京都見廻組の奴ら、厄介だな。\n"
"さっさとケリをつけて近藤を探さなくては……\n"
"こんなところで時間を取られている場合ではない。"
msgstr ""
"The Kyoto Mimawarigumi guys are awkward. I have to quickly find Kondo with a"
" button ... It's not the case when I'm spending time in such a place."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_129"
msgid ""
"沖田には悪いが今は一刻を争う。\n"
"京都見廻組は沖田に任せて、俺は近藤を探そう！"
msgstr ""
"It's bad for Okita, but now it's time to fight. Leave the Kyoto Mimawarigumi"
" to Okita, and I'll look for Kondo!"

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_130"
msgid ""
"原田……どこまでも性根の腐った奴だ。\n"
"真の剣術がいかなるものか\n"
"身をもってわからせてやろう……！"
msgstr ""
"Harada: He's a rotten guy with sexual roots. Let's get a feel for what true "
"swordsmanship is ...!"

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_131"
msgid ""
"新選組が火をつけて回ってるってのは\n"
"本当だったようだ。近藤の真意が気になるな。\n"
"早く近藤を見つけ出さなくては……"
msgstr ""
"It seems that it was true that the Shinsengumi was igniting. Don't worry "
"about Kondo's true intentions. I have to find Kondo early ..."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_132"
msgid ""
"近藤に手をだした奴は御所で俺を待っているらしい。\n"
"一体、何者なんだ……!?\n"
"急いで御所へ向かおう……！"
msgstr ""
"It seems that the guy who reached out to Kondo is waiting for me at the "
"Imperial Palace. Who the hell are you ...!? Let's hurry to the Imperial "
"Palace ...!"

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_133"
msgid ""
"以蔵……\n"
"ついにお前との決着をつける時が来たようだな。\n"
"坂本龍馬として全力で挑んでやる！"
msgstr ""
"Izo ... It seems that it's finally time to settle with you. I will do my "
"best as Ryoma Sakamoto!"

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_134"
msgid ""
"第十二章「京炎上」～完～\n"
"第十三章「龍馬暗殺」へ……"
msgstr "Chapter 12 \"Jingyan 1\" ~ End ~ Chapter 13 \"Ryoma Assassination\" へ..."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_135"
msgid ""
"今のうちにできる事をしておいた方が良さそうだ。\n"
"中岡と藤堂から連絡があるまで寺田屋で\n"
"体を休めておくか。"
msgstr ""
"It seems better to do what you can do now. Do you want to rest at Teradaya "
"until Nakaoka and Todo contact you?"

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_136"
msgid ""
"今のうちにできる事をしておいた方が良さそうだ。\n"
"別宅の様子を見に行っておくとしよう。"
msgstr ""
"It seems better to do what you can do now. Let's go to see the state of the "
"separate house."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_137"
msgid ""
"中岡が戻ったらしい。\n"
"２階へ行って話を聞こう。"
msgstr "Nakaoka seems to have returned. Let's go upstairs and listen."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_138"
msgid ""
"幾松のいる店へ急ごう。\n"
"確か松之井は伏見の蔵町にあったはずだ。"
msgstr ""
"Let's hurry to the store where Ikumatsu is. Certainly Matsunoi must have "
"been in Fushimi's Kuramachi."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_139"
msgid ""
"本当にふざけた奴だ。この刀で思い知らせてやる。\n"
"藤堂の想い、無駄にするわけにはいかない。"
msgstr ""
"He's a really playful guy. I'll let you know with this sword. Todo's "
"feelings cannot be wasted."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_140"
msgid ""
"作戦の時は明日の夜……\n"
"今のうちに十分支度しておかなくては……\n"
"何が待ち受けているのか分からないからな。"
msgstr ""
"At the time of the operation, tomorrow night ... I have to prepare enough "
"now ... I don't know what is waiting."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_141"
msgid ""
"作戦の時は夜……\n"
"今のうちに十分支度しておかなくては……\n"
"何が待ち受けているのか分からないからな。"
msgstr ""
"At night during the operation ... I have to prepare enough now ... I don't "
"know what's waiting."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_142"
msgid ""
"いよいよだな。\n"
"何が待ち受けているのか分からない。\n"
"出かける前に十分支度しておかなくてはな。"
msgstr ""
"It's finally time. I don't know what's waiting. You have to be well prepared"
" before you go out."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_143"
msgid ""
"いよいよだ。出かけるとしよう。\n"
"気を引き締めて行かなくては……"
msgstr "It's finally time. Let's go out. I have to be careful ..."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_144"
msgid ""
"もう一人の「坂本龍馬」の正体を、ついに\n"
"確かめる時が来たようだ……　真実をこの目で\n"
"見るまではやられるわけにはいかない！"
msgstr ""
"It seems that it's finally time to confirm the identity of the other \"Ryoma"
" Sakamoto\" ... You can't do it until you see the truth with your own eyes!"

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_145"
msgid ""
"第十三章「龍馬暗殺」～完～\n"
"最終章「夜明け」へ……"
msgstr "Chapter 13 \"Assassination of Ryoma\" -End-To the final chapter \"Dawn\" ..."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_146"
msgid ""
"お登勢、それにおりょうには世話になった。\n"
"最後に挨拶位はしておかないとな……\n"
"寺田屋に顔を出すとしよう。"
msgstr ""
"Thank you for your support. Lastly, I have to say hello ... Let's say I'm "
"going to Teradaya."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_147"
msgid ""
"まったく沖田にお登勢まで……　とんだ世話焼きだな。\n"
"土佐へ立つ前におりょうとの時間を作るとするか。\n"
"支度ができたら、お登勢に声をかけよう。"
msgstr ""
"It's completely up to Okita ... It's a great caretaker. Do you want to make "
"time with Ryo before you stand in Tosa? When you're ready, let's call out to"
" the climb."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_148"
msgid ""
"手始めにどこかの飯屋で腹ごなししよう。\n"
"おりょうを連れていくならどの店がいいだろうか？"
msgstr ""
"Let's get hungry at a restaurant somewhere to start. Which store would you "
"like to take with you?"

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_149"
msgid ""
"さて、腹もふくれたし軽く一杯いきたいとこだな。\n"
"おりょうが飲んでいるところは見たことがないが……\n"
"まぁ大丈夫だろう。"
msgstr ""
"By the way, I'm bloated and want to have a light drink. I've never seen Ryo "
"drinking, but ... well, that's okay."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_150"
msgid ""
"次は歌声酒場にでも行くか。\n"
"あそこなら、おりょうも楽しめるだろう。"
msgstr ""
"Would you like to go to the singing bar next time? You can enjoy Narasaki "
"over there."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_151"
msgid ""
"うまい飯、酒、それに歌ときたら後は舞だな。\n"
"にちぶ座へ行って、俺の舞を披露しよう。"
msgstr ""
"Good food, sake, and singing, then dance. Let's go to Nichibu-za and show "
"off my dance."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_152"
msgid ""
"おりょうと京の町を十分楽しめたな。\n"
"さて、土佐へ旅立つ前のお参りもかねて、\n"
"清水寺へ行くとしよう。"
msgstr ""
"I really enjoyed the town of Oryo and Kyoto. Now, let's go to Kiyomizu-dera "
"as a visit before leaving for Tosa."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_153"
msgid ""
"京でやり残したことはないだろうか？\n"
"土佐へ立つまであまり時間がない、\n"
"屯所で沖田、永倉、土方と刀の稽古をしておくか。"
msgstr ""
"Have you left behind in Kyo? I don't have much time to stand in Tosa, should"
" I practice Okita, Nagakura, Hijikata and swords at the tunsho?"

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_154"
msgid ""
"京でやり残したことはないだろうか？\n"
"土佐へ立つ支度ができたら、\n"
"屯所にいる沖田たちに声をかけて出発しよう。"
msgstr ""
"Have you left behind in Kyo? When you are ready to stand in Tosa, let's talk"
" to Okita and his friends at the tunsho and leave."

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_155"
msgid ""
"土佐はすっかり変わってしまったようだ……\n"
"嘆いている暇はない、武市の待つ高知城へ向かおう！"
msgstr ""
"Tosa seems to have changed completely ... I have no time to mourn, let's "
"head to Kochi Castle where Takeshi is waiting!"

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_156"
msgid ""
"京都見廻組まで来ているとはな……\n"
"だがここで足止めをくっている場合ではない！"
msgstr ""
"I don't think I've come to the Kyoto Mimawarigumi ... but it's not the case "
"when I'm stuck here!"

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_157"
msgid ""
"今は永倉を信じて先に進むしかなさそうだ。\n"
"武市の待つ高知城を目指そう！"
msgstr ""
"Now I have no choice but to believe in Nagakura and move on. Let's aim for "
"Kochi Castle where Takeshi is waiting!"

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_158"
msgid ""
"伊東率いる御陵衛士まで現れるとは……\n"
"奴にどんな恨みがあろうが知ったことではない。\n"
"今は前に進むだけだ！"
msgstr ""
"Even the Imperial Guard, led by Ito, would appear ... I didn't know what "
"kind of grudge he had. Now just move forward!"

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_159"
msgid ""
"悪いがここは土方に任せて先に進むしかなさそうだ。\n"
"武市の待つ高知城を目指そう！"
msgstr ""
"I'm sorry, but it seems that Hijikata has no choice but to move on. Let's "
"aim for Kochi Castle where Takeshi is waiting!"

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_160"
msgid ""
"こいつが貿易商のグラバー……　しかしどんな兵器を\n"
"出されようが、ここで引き下がるわけにはいかない！\n"
"何としてもここを突破しなくては！"
msgstr ""
"This guy is a trader's grabber ... But no matter what weapons he puts out, "
"he can't withdraw here! I have to break through here anyway!"

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_161"
msgid ""
"沖田……　すまない！\n"
"だが、俺はもう後戻りはできない……\n"
"武市の待つ高知城を目指そう！"
msgstr ""
"Okita ... I'm sorry! However, I can't go back anymore ... Let's aim for "
"Kochi Castle where Takeshi is waiting!"

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_162"
msgid ""
"兄弟……　今が勝負の時だ。\n"
"俺は全力で挑む！"
msgstr "Brothers ... Now is the time for the game. I will do my best!"

msgctxt "EXPLANATION_163"
msgid ""
"「龍が如く 維新！」クリアです。\n"
"お疲れ様でした。"
msgstr "\"Ryu ga Gotoku Restoration!\" Is clear. Thank you for your hard work."
